Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Vientiane, January 15 (KPL) -- There were last year 
three Chinese companies coming to make investment in the 
province of Oudomsai, with a total value of more than US $1 
million. 
  The Chinese companies are from Sibsong Panna, Yunnan, and 
Simao. The wholly Chinese investment was in the fields of 
services, hotel and restaurant. 
  According to the regulations concerning foreign investment 
in 
Laos, foreign investment ventures will be transferred to the Lao 
side upon the termination of a 15-year agreement. 

